违公序良俗，因此对温某的死亡承担轻微的民事赔偿责任，即承担 5% 的责任。无证据证明饭店经营者邬某存在过错行为，邬某不承担赔偿责任。 兴宁市人民法院一审判决同桌七人对温某的死亡承担 5% 的连带赔偿责任，即 52184 元，饭店老板不承担责任。原、被告提起上诉，梅州市中级人民法院二审维持原判。男子饭局上主动敬酒后，猝死！同桌人是否需承担责任？法院这样判... | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-6744478191d9855cc311fe636f67a659_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "135 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/515769390"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7/GZ1KrPw4sGEAMaCDc2ODk2OTQ4IIn8kpAGMBA43AFAGXIJNTE1NzY5MzkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "26_1644822152.0154366", "card_id": "Q_514726169", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 42}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "第一次买黄金戒指，应该选择像周大福老凤祥这种大品牌店，还是去同学妈妈开的黄金珠宝店？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "就怕小品牌的私人店会不会有参假，黄金不纯的问题。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-16a478008791b5bee193256781a0d393_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "134 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/514726169"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I7/GZ1KrPw4sGEAMaCDc2NjY0OTUxIPq6848GMAQ4Z0Aacgk1MTQ3MjYxNjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1644822152.0158489", "card_id": "Q_515673479", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 123}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "预算 5000-6000 左右，买安卓顶级旗舰还是买 iPhone 13？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "五千左右就能买到一加 10pro 小米 12pro iQOO9pro 还有上代的小米 11Ultra，至于平时嘛日常用的多偶尔打打游戏刷刷剧"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-502e7aa9354ca7e2191d4d0ca78e48d2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "124 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/515673479"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I7/GZ1KrPw4sGEAMaCDc2ODc1NjM0IN/cj5AGMAo4sAFAG3IJNTE1NjczNDc5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmT